plot:
Across six episodes, with three separate stories per episodes, we will 
reveal deaths that will make you marvel, fear and cry, from the bible 
salesman who is struck by lightning under a cloudless sky to the pet 
lover who falls into a cat dish with less than three-inches of water; 
from a brick-layer who is provoked to laugh for 25 minutes straight to a
 French tailor who tests an experimental glider off the Eiffel Tower. 
All are totally different in their inception, but all have the same 
fatal result.
title: Curious and Unusual Deaths
